## Privacy & Security

### Content Redaction
After sending digests:
- All `DigestItem.content` is replaced with `"[REDACTED]"`
- Preserves audit trail without storing sensitive data
- Original emails remain in Gmail

### Unsubscribe System
- Each digest includes secure unsubscribe token
- Users can opt out without account access
- Tokens are cryptographically secure

