## Troubleshooting

### Common Issues

**Digests not sending:**
- Check user has premium subscription
- Verify account is >4 days old
- Confirm frequency settings are valid

**AI summarization failing:**
- Check OpenAI API key and credits
- Verify email content is not empty
- Review error logs in QStash dashboard

**Duplicate digest items:**
- Ensure unique constraints are working
- Check for race conditions in upsert logic
- Verify messageId/threadId are correct

